title: Torreblanca Feat. Iraida Noriega "Have Yourself A Merry Little Christmas"
description:
Mexico City’s Torreblanca with guest vocalist Iraida Noriega contribute a beautiful cover of the classic “Have Yourself a Merry Little Christmas” to Converse Rubber Tracks’ holiday music EP, Noise To the World 2. Mastered by Grammy-Nominated engineer Mike Bozzi.

Produced and mixed by: Torreblanca
Music and Lyrics by: Torreblanca
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman
